00:18:51.750 --> 00:18:54.480
maaaring pagalingin ng acupuncture
ang gayong matigas na karamdaman.

00:18:54.920 --> 00:18:56.790
Miracle Doctor Fei,
kung hindi mo ako masyadong mapurol,

00:18:56.790 --> 00:18:58.440
maaari mo ba akong turuan
ng acupuncture techniques?

00:18:58.440 --> 00:18:59.440
Paano kung ako, sa ngalan mo,

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:01.440
gawin ang paggamot sa aking kapatid na babae?

00:19:02.880 --> 00:19:03.510
T-Iyon ay…

00:19:06.590 --> 00:19:08.030
Kung gusto mo akong turuan,

00:19:08.030 --> 00:19:10.060
Mag-aalok ako ng tatlong teal ng ginto

00:19:10.200 --> 00:19:11.660
at maging iyong alagad.

00:19:12.830 --> 00:19:14.570
Hindi na kailangan ng ginto.

00:19:14.680 --> 00:19:16.680
Hindi ako kapos sa pera.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:18.640
Ang asawa mo

00:19:18.750 --> 00:19:20.880
ay kaibigan ni Lu Lingfeng pagkatapos ng lahat.

00:19:20.920 --> 00:19:21.680
Bukod,

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:24.240
kapatid ang tingin ni Xijun sayo.

00:19:26.110 --> 00:19:28.830
Sabi mo minsan natuto ka ng acupuncture.

00:19:29.400 --> 00:19:31.590
Kung alam mo lamang ang mga pangunahing kaalaman,

00:19:31.680 --> 00:19:33.270
tapos tinuturuan ka

00:19:33.310 --> 00:19:34.920
magiging medyo mahirap.

00:19:37.480 --> 00:19:38.340
Paano ito?

00:19:38.590 --> 00:19:40.270
