00:31:18.760 --> 00:31:20.560
Mangyaring parusahan sila, Sheriff Du.

00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:22.000
Paano ka nila na-provoke?

00:31:22.000 --> 00:31:23.590
Namimigay sila ng butil at alak

00:31:23.590 --> 00:31:25.130
ngunit sadyang ibukod

00:31:25.200 --> 00:31:26.680
ang mga ipinanganak sa maharlika.

00:31:26.680 --> 00:31:27.740
Sinadya nilang gumawa ng conflict.

